The paper focuses on video story question-answering using a multimodal dual attention mechanism, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves machine learning (ML) techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
